### AI Query System - REST API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension or copy to test-ai-api.rest

# ============================================
# GENERAL QUERIES
# ============================================

### General Query - Natural Language
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Show me all students in class 5A",
  "userId": "65a123abc456"
}

###

### General Query - Student Details
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/query
Content-Type: application/json

